                                <Property name="messageText" type="java.lang.String" value="&lt;html&gt;Exports the animation in format &quot;allyanimationXXX.bin&quot; or &quot;enemyanimationXXX.bin.&lt;br&gt;By default, ally animations 0-39 are &lt;i&gt;attack&lt;/&gt; animations, 40-79 are &lt;i&gt;dodge&lt;/&gt; animations, 80+ for &lt;i&gt;special&lt;/&gt; animations.&lt;br&gt;See &lt;b&gt;SF2Enums&lt;/b&gt; &quot;; enum AllyBattleAnimations&quot;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;By default, enemy animations 0-59 are &lt;i&gt;attack&lt;/&gt; animations, 60-117 are &lt;i&gt;dodge&lt;/&gt; animations, 118+ for &lt;i&gt;special&lt;/&gt; animations.&lt;br&gt;See &lt;b&gt;SF2Enums&lt;/b&gt; &quot;; enum EnemyBattleAnimations&quot;.&lt;/html&gt;"/>
                                <Property name="text" type="java.lang.String" value=""/>
                              </Properties>
                            </Component>
